      <ref link="desktop api user interaction functions">User Interaction (UI) Functions</ref>
      <ref link="UI_SELECT_COLOR2 Function">UI_SELECT_COLOR2()</ref>
      <ref>Color Functions and Methods</ref>
   </see>
